# Healthcare Workforce Management Platform

**System Definition & Feature Specification**

This document defines the **complete functionality, modules, roles, and features** of the Healthcare Workforce Management Platform based on the SRS.

The system is designed to help healthcare organizations manage **staff scheduling, workforce operations, compliance, and workforce analytics**.

---

# 1. System Overview

The Healthcare Workforce Management Platform enables hospitals and healthcare facilities to:

* Manage healthcare staff
* Schedule shifts efficiently
* Track attendance and working hours
* Ensure credential compliance
* Manage shift swaps and time-off requests
* Monitor workforce analytics
* Maintain staffing ratios and operational efficiency

The platform supports **role-based access control (RBAC)**.

---

# 2. System Roles

The system has **three primary roles**.

## 2.1 Admin

Admin users have **full system control**.

### Responsibilities

* Manage users and staff
* Configure departments and units
* Monitor workforce analytics
* Manage compliance rules
* Manage credentials and policies
* Configure system settings

### Admin Features

* Create staff accounts
* Update staff profiles
* Assign staff roles
* Manage departments
* Manage units
* View workforce analytics
* Monitor staffing ratios
* Manage credential requirements
* Manage system settings
* View system-wide reports

---

## 2.2 Manager

Managers oversee **staff operations within their department or unit**.

### Responsibilities

* Manage schedules
* Assign shifts
* Monitor attendance
* Approve requests
* Ensure staffing coverage

### Manager Features

* View department staff directory
* Create shift schedules
* Assign staff to shifts
* Approve shift swaps
* Approve time-off requests
* Monitor staff attendance
* Monitor overtime
* View department analytics

---

## 2.3 Staff

Staff users include **nurses, doctors, technicians, and healthcare workers**.

### Responsibilities

* View schedules
* Track work hours
* Request shift swaps
* Submit time-off requests

### Staff Features

* View assigned shifts
* Clock in and clock out
* Submit shift swap requests
* Submit time-off requests
* View personal profile
* Upload credentials
* Update availability

---

# 3. System Modules

The system is divided into several **functional modules**.

---

# 4. Authentication & Authorization Module

This module manages **user login and role-based access**.

## Features

* Email/password login
* Supabase authentication
* Role-based access control
* Session management
* Secure route protection
* Automatic dashboard redirection

## Dashboard Redirection

Admin → `/dashboard/admin`
Manager → `/dashboard/manager`
Staff → `/dashboard/staff`

---

# 5. Staff Management Module

This module manages **healthcare staff profiles and professional information**.

## Features

* Staff directory
* Staff profile management
* Skills tracking
* Credential management
* Department assignment
* Contact information management
* Availability scheduling

## Staff Directory

The directory includes:

* Name
* Role
* Department
* Employment type
* Status

Features:

* Search
* Filter by department
* Filter by role
* Pagination

## Staff Profile

Each staff member has a profile containing:

Personal Information

* Name
* Email
* Phone

Professional Information

* Role
* Department
* Unit
* Skills

Credentials

* Certifications
* License expiration

Availability

* Weekly availability schedule

---

# 6. Department & Unit Management Module

Healthcare organizations operate with **multiple departments and units**.

Examples:

* Emergency
* ICU
* Surgery
* Pediatrics

## Features

* Create departments
* Create hospital units
* Assign staff to departments
* Assign staff to units
* Manage department hierarchy

---

# 7. Shift Scheduling Module

This module manages **staff shift scheduling**.

## Features

* Create shifts
* Assign staff to shifts
* Manage schedule calendar
* Track open shifts
* Update schedules
* Real-time schedule updates

## Shift Information

Each shift includes:

* Start time
* End time
* Department
* Assigned staff
* Shift status

---

# 8. Shift Swap Module

Allows staff to **exchange shifts with other staff members**.

## Features

* Request shift swap
* Accept swap request
* Manager approval
* Track swap status

## Swap Workflow

1. Staff requests swap
2. Another staff accepts
3. Manager approves

---

# 9. Time Tracking Module

This module tracks **staff working hours and attendance**.

## Features

* Clock in
* Clock out
* Break tracking
* Overtime calculation
* Work history

## Time Entry Data

* Clock in time
* Clock out time
* Break duration
* Overtime hours

---

# 10. Time-Off Request Module

Staff can request **leave or vacation**.

## Features

* Submit PTO request
* Submit sick leave request
* Track request status
* Manager approval workflow

## Request Status

* Pending
* Approved
* Rejected

---

# 11. Credential & License Tracking Module

Healthcare workers require **valid certifications and licenses**.

## Features

* Store certification records
* Upload documents
* Track expiration dates
* Send expiration alerts

## Examples

* Nursing License
* CPR Certification
* Medical License

---

# 12. Notification System

The platform sends **system notifications** to users.

## Notification Types

* Schedule updates
* Shift swap approvals
* Time-off approvals
* Credential expiration alerts

Notifications can appear as:

* In-app notifications
* Toast alerts

---

# 13. Manager Dashboard Module

Managers have a **department-level dashboard**.

## Dashboard Metrics

* Department staff count
* Open shifts
* Pending approvals
* Overtime hours
* Shift coverage

---

# 14. Admin Dashboard Module

Admin dashboard provides **organization-wide analytics**.

## Dashboard Metrics

* Total staff
* Departments overview
* Credential expiration alerts
* Staffing compliance
* Workforce utilization
* Overtime analytics

---

# 15. Staff Dashboard Module

Staff dashboard shows **personal workforce information**.

## Dashboard Widgets

* Upcoming shifts
* Work hours
* Credentials
* Shift swap requests
* Time-off requests

---

# 16. Reporting & Analytics Module

Provides workforce insights.

## Reports

* Staff utilization
* Overtime analysis
* Shift coverage
* Credential compliance
* Department workforce metrics

---

# 17. Core Database Entities

The system includes the following main entities:

* Users
* Staff
* Departments
* Units
* Skills
* Credentials
* Staff Skills
* Staff Credentials
* Availability
* Shifts
* Shift Assignments
* Time Entries
* Time-Off Requests
* Shift Swap Requests
* Notifications

---

# 18. System Architecture

Technology Stack

Frontend

* Next.js
* TypeScript
* TailwindCSS
* ShadCN UI

Backend

* Supabase
* PostgreSQL
* Supabase Auth
* Supabase Storage

Forms

* React Hook Form
* Zod validation

Notifications

* Sonner toast

---

# 19. Security

The system uses **Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)**.

Access Rules

Admin

* Full access

Manager

* Department-level access

Staff

* Access to personal data only

Row Level Security (RLS) is implemented in Supabase.

---

# 20. MVP Scope

The first version of the system includes:

* Authentication
* Staff management
* Department management
* Shift scheduling
* Time tracking
* Shift swap requests
* Time-off requests
* Manager dashboard

---

# 21. Future Enhancements

Possible advanced features:

* AI shift scheduling
* Predictive staffing
* Staff burnout analytics
* Mobile workforce app
* AI staffing recommendations

---

# 22. Conclusion

This platform provides a **complete workforce management solution for healthcare organizations**.

Key benefits:

* Efficient workforce scheduling
* Compliance with healthcare regulations
* Reduced overtime costs
* Improved staff satisfaction
* Better operational visibility
